This is exactly the thing to do.  If you use words only, you have a great 
start.  If you restrict it to common words, and real sentence structures, 
you have an even better start.  

If you use distributed entropy all over the book, which is then really 
independent, you are sol except for the fact that someday sooner than 
people thing every book will be digitized.

